column3: “This strain is one of the best I've ever tasted. Great High.”
“The word Alpha has a meaning, and this strain was named accordingly. Another High Times award winner from alpha medic a multi cup winning collective.”
“Best sleep I've had in a long time thanks to this strain. It taste great and its just wuderbar :D”
“This bud is absolute dank. Sticky icky at its finest”
“Damn! Nuff said. Pretty buds, dense and full of tri's..definitely looks what a con issuer would want. will smack you hard. If this was a 12  woofer
column4: Windows would shatter from the hit. Highly recommend”"

column3: “Nice, functional head high. Smooth flavor, spicy without being overpowering.”
“Lovely strain that's ideal if you want an evening high. I'd suggest for everybody!”
“Alpha Og is an freaking amazing indica! soft flower and such amazing taste and smell! if your looking for an outstanding indica I would go with the Alpha Og all day! honestly best body high ever”
“Had this in wax form, very very good balanced hybrid high and flavor”

“An easy peasy bud with an imagination for relaxation. On this the hyperventilating hosts of YouTube make sense, as they slow down but remain consistent. The world glows with opportunity. I love my life.”

“think of OG Kush, but with an extra gear. nose is similar to GSC, good and doughy with a hint of pine and lemon. turned me into a space cadet with the meanest dry eyes ever, save this for when you ain't got shit to do for sure.”

“ALPHA OG is AWESOME!!!
Nice smooth burn with light spicy flavour. 
Slow light buzz at first and then it hits quick with nice mellow high. 
Had a amazing sleep! 😴”
“Excellent for evenings or bedtime, overall superb.”
“This bud was delicious. Great high. Very happy and uplifted from this bud. It went will with Xbox and a beef,”
“Its a good high and I like the taste!”
“a wonder to gaze into, great smell, big fluffy buds. smokes well, the high is decent.”
“Definitely one of the best strains in the last 5/6 years!”

“Delicious, potent, and an extremely heavy hitter — Alpha OG is not one to be messed with. I picked this up based on smell alone and was extremely satisfied. With a fresh, earthy taste, it feels like you're taking a breath of pine forest air and hits silky smooth. Boasting a fairly dynamic high, an excellent peak, and a euphoric come down, Alpha OG is a great strain to keep in rotation.”
“I love this stuff I will buy it again”
“This strain is always fire. Always consistent. Great High!”
“Fire ass shit good high good chill night w your girl.”
“One of San Diego's finest OGs”

“Perfect strain for those days where you find yourself coming home from work exhausted and worn out. Helps with mind racing thoughts and uplifts mood. Overall one of my favorites so far to smoke at the end of your day. It’s helps make the next day bearable.”

“This strain is incredible, just won 1st place potency at the 2017 San Diego Farmers Market! Alpha medic puts out some of the best strains in San Diego, and this alpha is the top of the line. Don't miss out on this multiple award winner!!!🔥🔥🔥”

“good one I've come across,
 unfortunately for me my sinus is jacked as I smoke it, but it did get rid of the headache”

“Beautifully structured nugs covered in trichomes with short red hairs scattered throughout these flowers. After two bong rips I'm feeling relaxed but able to stay focused on whatever I choose. This would be a strain that I'd smoke before bed forsure. Definitely potent. This nug has many different scents to it ranging from diesel to mint to that earthy og scent.”
“Pretty solid high but makes you pretty sleepy”
“Definitely one of the most bomb strains i've ever had. Thought it may have been just me, but then i picked some up for some friends and they thought it was fire too!”
“Chilling on a Friday with the homies.  Super relaxed and chill high.  Very dreamy feeling.  Recommended for a fun night.”
“potent”

“Got a pretty good body high from this strain, made me feel pretty stoney, helped with sleep but didn’t put me to sleep, slight munchies but controllable, was too relaxed to make it to the kitchen. If you’re an indica heavy hybrid fan Alpha is probably for you.”
“best og ever. alpha medic is my go to spot. so lucky to be in SD where they are. best collective around in my humble opinion”

“Phenomenal strain. Super dank, heavy on the indica side but not overwhelming. First time ever getting a hybrid as I'm usually an indica kind of smoker but this is phenomenal. Would I get it again? Eh, I'll pass. But I'm not dissapointed with it at all and am enjoying every last bowl.”
“This bud was delicious. Great high. Very happy and uplifted from this bud. It went will with Xbox and a beef,”
“very ery good high great nap after”
“Alpha OG is the best”
